# Ignore everything by default, so swapped-in scanned book folders and
# generated artifacts are never accidentally committed.
*

# --- Track the tool and its docs ---
!.gitignore
!README.md
!ocr_books.py
!requirements.txt
!Dockerfile

# --- Let `entire enable` manage its own artifacts / agent hooks ---
# For a darthzen sync these stay committed; for any other remote use
# `entire enable --local` (writes gitignored settings.local.json).
!.entire/
!.claude/
